filmes-frontend/.pnp.js

# General
**/.DS_Store
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.git
